title: 820-01700-A Not turn on
message:
Macbook does not turn on.
have
PPDCIN_G3H = 5v
PPBUS_G3H = 1.02v
Apparently there is no short to ground.

title: 820-01700-A Not turn on
message:
Post diode mode to ground at PPBUS_G3H (not L7030) and 3V3_G3H_RTC (L6960/61).
PPBUS_G3H is the first voltage to appear on the board.

If you get 5V at R7020, then post U7000 basic voltages; P_IN, AUX_DET, VDDA/P, EN_MVR, CBC_ON, A/BMON.
